  "id": "RAW_cb0d621e",
  "title": "从零到千万：一个中国开源操作系统的全球崛起之路",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4MTQ4NjQzMw==&mid=2652793549&idx=1&sn=22473d64bcd2d1ebac14adb75380ee8b",
  "date": "2025-12-01 10:02:00",
  "author": "智东西",
  "siteName": "智东西",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: top;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=838a7b2e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgClYviaAPicT05Hxbx2npnHWibVU6UC8TkYaoofh85pxIbXFNDWgXyZ5EC2RYqjr4JkicNVuU3icdCyJQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 15px 8px 35px;\">\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: normal;font-size: 15px;padding: 0 10px;border-left: 3.5px solid #00b0ec;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">OpenEuler社区全球开发者PR数已达24万。</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 7.5px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">作者 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 49px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">王涵</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 35px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编辑 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 49px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">漠影</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">操作系统七十余年的发展，是计算技术演进最直接的体现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其职能范围从早期解析纸带指令、管理单机软硬件资源，逐步演进为调度分布式云环境中的异构算力、协同从数据中心到边缘侧的全球终端设备。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一持续的技术演进路径，清晰地记录了计算范式从封闭、孤立的专用系统，向泛在分布与智能协同方向发展的全过程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如今，随着AI大模型技术掀起新一轮产业浪潮，计算架构与软件栈正面临重构，操作系统作为底层核心软件，再次处于关键演进节点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这一背景下，中国开源社区的代表——</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">开放原子开源欧拉（OpenAtom openEuler）</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，正积极参与到新一代操作系统的构建中，尝试为AI驱动的基础软件形态提供新的思路与实现路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">从内部积淀到全球共建</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">openEuler的六年演进之路</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">openEuler的前身其实是华为内部项目。2019年，全球技术博弈加剧，华为宣布</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">开源</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">并上线openEuler社区，12月31日，openEuler</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">首行代码正式开放。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从此，中国</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">首个</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">面向数字基础设施的开源操作系统正式诞生，开启了其从企业自用向社区共建的转型之路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2020年3月，openEuler发布首个长期支持版本20.03 LTS，具备规模商用能力；同年9月发布首个创新版20.09，由此确立</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“创新版每半年更新、LTS版每两年更新”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的双轨发布模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2021年11月，华为将openEuler全量代码</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">捐赠</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">给开放原子开源基金会，这一动作让openEuler从企业主导的开源项目，正式转变为</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">产业共建、社区自治</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的开源项目。同年，openEuler 21.03创新版发布，实现内核热升级等创新特性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2022年6月，麒麟软件、SUSE等9家企业发布基于openEuler 22.03 LTS的商业发行版，新增原创代码</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">4.8万行</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，软件包总量达</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">28087个</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，还首次实现对服务器、云计算等四大场景的全场景融合支持，推动社区技术成果走向</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">商业化落地</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.379\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=24064c40&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgPaFP7NGjEqtTyruruMwgO3hEzzcE7U2TQD2UqF9edR0Pybgibas1RoicwjyYiaQNLUIXcibNeksX4xw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年9月30日，openEuler 25.09创新版正式发布，该版本基于Linux 6.6内核，面向服务器、云原生与嵌入式场景，带来了包括内核优化、众核高密、机密容器/虚机等在内的功能扩展。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在11月15日举办的开放原子操作系统大会上，openEuler发布了</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">全球首个面向超节点的操作系统openEuler 24.03 LTS SP3</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，并明确该系统需具备全局资源抽象、异构资源融合等核心特征，以此释放超节点算力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI浪潮汹涌</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">openEuler做出了“超节点的OS”</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">随着大模型参数规模从千亿级向万亿级迈进，传统服务器集群的算力瓶颈日益凸显。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为应对这一挑战，科技巨头纷纷推出新一代</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">超节点</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">解决方案：华为推出昇腾Atlas 900 PoD，单个集群可提供高达256 PFLOPS的FP16算力；英伟达发布的DGX SuperPOD通过NVLink全互联架构，实现了GPU间的高速通信；英特尔则推出Gaudi 3集群，专门针对大模型训练场景优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">超节点不仅是一个更大规模的服务器集群，更是一个需要全局资源管理和智能调度的新型计算实体。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而传统的软件架构在面对超节点时，暴露出资源调度效率低、异构算力利用不充分、系统级优化不足等问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就要求底层操作系统必须重新思考其架构设计，从传统的单机资源管理，转向跨节点的全域资源抽象与调度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">面对这场变革，openEuler今年下定决心，要</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“全面拥抱AI，成为超节点的OS”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，如何将这一目标付诸实践？openEuler的路线图已经清晰，可以概括为“三步走”：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先是</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">前瞻性地预留接口。</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">这一点，openEuler在2024年3月发布的24.03版本中已经实现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其次是</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">推动能力与框架的深度融合</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。按照规划，openEuler将在2025年底前开放操作系统内部的基础框架，2026年上半年完成配套工具链建设，实现与硬件厂商的同步发布。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后是</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">打通商业化路径。</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">openEuler正与麒麟软件、统信软件等合作伙伴携手，将社区版转化为可商用的成熟版本。这项工作的全面落地，将成为openEuler在2026年的重点推进方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">面向数据中心场景，openEuler社区还带来了全新的</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Intelligence BooM全栈开源AI解决方案</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。这个方案是openEuler与高校、企业及各技术社区共同打造的成果，目标很明确，即构建一个开放的AI生态，帮助各行各业实现智能化转型，让企业级AI应用不再遥不可及。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">继去年7月推出首个版本“2507烩面”后，Intelligence BooM这次全新升级的“2511敲鱼面”版本主打</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“低成本、高效率、易落地”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">三大特点，不仅支持超过50种模型的微调，还通过异构协同技术让推理效率提升了10%到30%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">更重要的是，它具备了快速适配AgenticAI 智能体生态的能力，让操作系统真正变得</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“原生智能”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.448\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36b50d45&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhXyDWciaa5ibsjzCZQuFOtCicsTRkNbNuSzPmZHwvVdUMe6cMicHa19yMmTJoFjUPwIEXO47olCv5O8w%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">从中国走向世界</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">openEuler如何融入国际开源体系？</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“共建、共享、共治”，是openEuler社区一直秉承的理念。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">openEuler融合了中西方文化优势，形成了</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“商业支撑+多元参与”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的社区模式：由企业主体保障交付质量与合规性，吸引专业力量投入，同时开放吸纳“为爱发电”的开发者，激发创新活力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">开源六年以来，openEuler社区发展迅速，截至目前，社区成员企业已超</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">2100家</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，贡献者突破</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">2.3万人</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，社区用户超过</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">550万</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，兼容ISV伙伴超</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">4000家</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，商业</span><span class=\"wx_search_keyword_wrap\"><span leaf=\"\">OSV</span></span><span leaf=\"\">达到</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">25家</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，全球开发者PR数达</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">24万</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不仅如此，openEuler社区还于去年提出</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“泛开源欧拉”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">模式。这个模式的思路很灵活：其他社区或项目可以根据自身需求，自由借鉴开源欧拉的技术模块组合使用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种开放包容的做法，让openEuler的技术价值能够在更广泛的场景中发挥作用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在全球开源组织协作层面，开源欧拉社区近期与Zephyr嵌入式技术基金会、Linux Foundation AI&amp;Data基金会达成深度技术合作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前，开源欧拉社区累计与</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">15家</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">全球开源组织在AI、云、大数据、HPC、嵌入式等领域建立紧密合作关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.342\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=760e2e17&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhXyDWciaa5ibsjzCZQuFOtCicdicpUpUYdNkulVux5sBXjWKzoBCGT593SQIhJZef4THGJk9ZiafVtNzw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">04</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：六年打磨，openEuler为全球开源生态持续贡献“中国智慧”</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">六年的发展，openEuler不仅实现了自身从技术雏形到产业标杆的蜕变，更走出了一条中国开源项目“自主创新、开放合作、全球共赢”的发展道路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从千万级装机量的市场认可，到全球范围内的生态共建，openEuler用实际成果证明，中国开源技术能够成为全球数智化转型的核心支撑。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细解读了中国开源操作系统 openEuler 从内部项目到全球共建的六年崛起之路，及其在 AI 浪潮下成为“超节点 OS”的战略布局。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细解读了中国开源操作系统 openEuler 从内部项目到全球共建的六年崛起之路，及其在 AI 浪潮下成为“超节点 OS”的战略布局。",
  "summary": "文章深入剖析了中国开源操作系统 openEuler 的六年发展历程。openEuler 起源于华为内部项目，于 2019 年正式开源，并在 2021 年捐赠给开放原子开源基金会，成功转型为产业共建、社区自治的开源项目。文章详细介绍了其“创新版每半年更新、LTS 版每两年更新”的双轨发布模式，以及商业发行版的落地情况。面对 AI 大模型带来的计算架构重构，openEuler 明确提出“全面拥抱 AI，成为超节点的 OS”的战略目标，通过预留接口、深度融合框架和打通商业化路径“三步走”策略，并推出了 Intelligence BooM 全栈开源 AI 解决方案，旨在构建开放 AI 生态，实现企业级 AI 应用的低成本、高效率、易落地。此外，文章还强调了 openEuler 通过“商业支撑+多元参与”模式和“泛开源欧拉”理念，积极融入国际开源体系，与全球 15 家开源组织建立合作，展现了中国开源智慧在全球舞台的贡献。",
